{"tid":1899400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★KONAMI「上上下下左右左右BA」設計師 橋本和久 逝世","createTime":"2020-02-26T14:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T03:51:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7d20ebffc5b6348d3af9687d9fbff57ba106cd83","tid":1899400,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"以「上上下下左右左右BA」而為玩家所知的「KONAMI秘技」，其發明者程式設計師橋本和久於昨晚逝世，目前尚未有官方與家人證實消息，來自於曾與他有工作交流的遊戲作曲家竹之內裕治，以推特帳號「TECHNOuchi 」揭露訃聞，目前許多玩家都在轉推哀悼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/3986941l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2F3986941l.jpg&h=757c125b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「KONAMI秘技」據說是橋本和久創在開發 1985 推出的遊戲《宇宙巡航艦 グラディウス》時，為了幫助玩家通關才設計此指令。之後在《魂斗羅》系列中更是頻繁被運用讓玩家擁有 30 條命，許多 KONAMI 開發的遊戲幾乎都使用了此彩蛋指令，就連小島秀夫的《潛龍諜影》系列、《星域毀滅者》都致敬過，宛如一種遊戲文化而廣為玩家知曉。讓這個特殊指令在不同平台間使用，更會作為一些網站的彩蛋元素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99285915/?fbclid=IwAR12ltvk2LIl33Bi_CQazmACEXg-hYCUZnv7-zZFf_dUQiS7L2ittqUYAE0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamebase.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ftopic%2F99285915%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR12ltvk2LIl33Bi_CQazmACEXg-hYCUZnv7-zZFf_dUQiS7L2ittqUYAE0&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=0e65e16a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99285915/?fbclid=IwAR12ltvk2LIl33Bi_CQazmACEXg-hYCUZnv7-zZFf_dUQiS7L2ittqUYAE0</a>"},{"pid":"eccf9cba96b741d124ec0c926c9ec9302b9fb33b","tid":1899400,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class